member.remarks:

Sample request body

             ```json
             {
               "student": {
                 "firstName": "Ioana",
                 "lastName":  "Marin",
                 "email":     "ioana.marin@student.ro",
                 "cnp":       "2990101223344",
                 "phone":     "0734567890",
                 "password":  "*Studentpass1"
               },
               "payment": {
                 "scholarshipBasePayment": true,
                 "sessionsPayed": 0
               },
               "file": {
                 "scholarshipStartDate":    "2024-04-25",
                 "criminalRecordExpiryDate": "2025-04-25",
                 "medicalRecordExpiryDate":  "2024-10-25",
                 "status":        "Draft",
                 "instructorId":  null,
                 "vehicleId":     null,
                 "teachingCategoryId": null
               }
             }
             ```

member.summary:
Generates a signed JWT access-token for a given user and
their roles.  Secret is taken from the JWT_KEY environment variable;
if absent it falls back to Jwt:Key from configuration files.
